{"tid":820480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大英帝國】山竹如箭在弦 處處都是米字窗","createTime":"2018-09-15T12:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T18:10:43.000Z","uid":23707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a982968a55d41ac7d614c953a9fd8beaa8acbd74","tid":820480,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T12:40:41.000Z","msg":"超強颱風「山竹」如箭在弦，直撲本港。連日來市民都在「等」颱風，儲糧食、貼玻璃窗，各式各樣。其中「天鴿」襲港期間成重災區的杏花邨，今日處處都見米字窗，管理處亦在停車場放置水泵水閘備用。<br />\n<br />\n今早記者到西灣河、鯉景灣一帶，住宅樓宇和地下商舖都貼上防風膠紙，連西灣河水警基地的玻璃窗，也用膠紙貼成X或米字。<br />\n<br />\n杏花邨居民潘太指，上次「天鴿」襲港，她的私家車滲在水中，幸沒有「死火」，要強行駛走。今次她早有準備，今早已經將它泊到日租停車場，預計泊到下周一，雖然收費不菲，唯有「當抄張牛肉乾」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，九龍灣多間車行的落地玻璃，亦貼上防風膠紙，為颶風吹襲作好準備。"},{"pid":"4d6979263c5153f9e05c0aeff5f52245454d470e","tid":820480,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T12:47:32.000Z","msg":"圖啦？"},{"pid":"cd1033ef7f895637e78bb0a51b5535fea6a83489","tid":820480,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T12:48:26.000Z","msg":"唔係英國旗就係蘇格蘭旗 大逆不道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d6856e211caea69316eba76c368cf9c3d4dc38","tid":820480,"uid":52429,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T18:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/16/020923_a98f68f1f457c3b800e4378d3515ea96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F16%2F020923_a98f68f1f457c3b800e4378d3515ea96.jpg&h=4d18fa2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/16/020943_9a842cbb71391754d4cb2a5d4745a78a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F16%2F020943_9a842cbb71391754d4cb2a5d4745a78a.jpg&h=3dd73845&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}